  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas Sihreeru Kehninsch\nbij fatweem Rattu Ahwersteem/\n(to bija trithsDefmits un Diwi)\npaweblejs un fazzijs: Ne lansee-\ntees prett ne kahdu jeb niasu jeb\nleelu/ ka prett to Israëta Kehni-\nnu ween.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu to Rattu Ahwer-\nsti Josawatu redseja/ tad fazziia\ntee: Teefcham tas irr tas Isra-\netka Kehninsch / un tee greeſahs/\nus winnu lausdamees/ bet Josa-\nwats brehze.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu to Rattu Ahwer-\nsti redseja/ ka schis tas Israëta\nKehninsch ne bija/ tad tee no wi-\nna atpakkat greeſahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet weens Wihrs uswil-\nke fawu Stohpu nonejauschi/ un\nschahwe to Israëta Kehnizu starp\ntahn Sprahdsehn un Kruhſchu-\nBrunnahin. Tad fazziawisch\nus fawu Ohrmanni: Greesta-\nwu Rohku/ un iswed d mañno ta\nLehgera/ jo es esinu eewainohts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta Rauschana wairo-\njahs tai Deena/ un tas Kehninsch\nstahweja us fatweem Ratteim\nteem Sihrezeem pretti/ un no-\nmirre Wakkara/ un tahs Wah-\ntes Affinis strehje Rattu Widdû.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad tappe Lehgeri is-\nfaukts/ kad ta Saule gribbeja\nno-eet/ un fazzihts: Ikkats lai\natgreeſahs us fawu Pilsfahtu\nun us fawu Semuni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta nomirre tas kehninsch/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad nu tee Ratti Santa-\nrijas Dihki masgati tappe / tad\nlaistja tee Sunniwinna Affinis.\nKur tahs Maukas (tohs) mas-\ngaja pehz ta KUNGA Wahrdü/\nko wiꞥſch bij runnajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 39,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas nu wehl no Akaba\nLeetahmatleek/ un wiſs/ ko wiꞥſch\ndarrijs/ un tas Elewantu-Kanlu\nNams/ ko wiꞥſch irr darrijs/ un\nwiſſi Pilsfahti/ ko wiꞥſch irr us-\ntaitijs/ tas wiſs irr rakstihts to\nIsraëta Kehnizu Laiku Grahi-\nmatā.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 40,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tā aismitge Akabs ar\nfatweem Tehveein / un Akasjus\nwinna Dehis tappe par Kehni-\nnu winna Weetā.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 41,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Josawats Afus Dehis\ntappe par Kehnizu pahr Juhdü/\nzettortā Gaddā Akaba ta Isra-\netka Kehnina.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 42,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Josawats bija triths-\ndefmits un veezus Gaddus wezz/\nkad wiꞥſch par Kehnizu tappe/\nun waldija dividefmitis un pee-\nzus Gaddus Jerusaleme. Un\nwinna Mahtei bija Asuba\nWahrdā/Silka Meita.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 43,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch staigaja us\nwiſſeem Zelkeem fawa Tehwa\nAfus/ wiꞥſch ne atstahjahs no\nteem / un darrija/ kas tam KUN-\nGAM patikfe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 44,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tatschu tee Augſtumi ne\ntappe nopohstiti / un tee Landis\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
